Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:08.70,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Kodoku na yoru eranda no ne hajimete jibun de\N(For the first time, I chose a lonely night)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:13.51,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Anata no step midareteru\N(Your steps are growing fainter)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:21.10,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Nagareru seaside breeze kokoro o shizumete\N(As the softly blowing seaside breeze calms my heart)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:27.78,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Omoide-iro ni somerarete yuku nagisa no balcony\N(This balcony overlooking the sea attains the hue of my memories)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:32.22,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Anata no kage tooku naru\N(And your shadow gradually fades)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:39.56,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hitomi tojireba baby kata o karite nemuritai yo\N(When I close my eyes, baby,)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.91,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hitomi tojireba baby kata o karite nemuritai yo\N(I want to fall asleep leaning on your shoulder)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:49.09,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai kedo ima koso say good bye\N(I want to hug you tight, but it's time to say good bye)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:52.27,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Midnight shout! I'm a Star dust
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.50,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Mayonaka no challenger\N(A midnight challenger)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:03:01.82,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Kinou yori tashika na ashita o tataku\N(I knock on the gate of tomorrow that's more certain than yesterday)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.99,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Midnight shout! Mystery dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.94,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hashiru koto yametara\N(As soon as I stop running)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:13.07,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah... yume wa yume no mama de owari sa\N(Ah, my dreams will fizzle out unfulfilled)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:16.14,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Midnight shout! Mystery dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.13,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hashiru koto yametara\N(As soon as I stop running)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:30.81,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah... yume wa yume no mama de owari sa\N(Ah, my dreams will fizzle out unfulfilled)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:23.05,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Mabuta wo tojitara\N(Once you close your eyes,)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.05,0:23:28.26,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Kimi no festa ga hajimaru\N(Your festa will begin)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:44.06,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Maketemo suteki na yuuki kitto wasurenai\N(Even if you lose, I won't forget your wonderful courage)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:56.53,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Senakagoshi ni ryoute ippai no smile for you\N(Look back, and you'll see a handful of smiles for you)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:24:09.02,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Koe ni naranai ai ga hajiketeru\N(My love surges out, though I can't put it into words)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:21.40,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Asa ga kuru made soba ni iteageru smile again\N(I will stay by your side until the dawn, so smile again)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.40,0:24:34.08,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hoshizora mo kimi no tame ni dake oritekita...\N(The starry cloak of night descended just for you...)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.28,0:46:13.70,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Kazoekirenai ai wo kono sora ni kazarou\N(I'll decorate the sky with countless displays of my love)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.51,0:46:21.57,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Itsuka kimi ni todoku you ni\N(I hope one day it reaches you)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.57,0:46:25.92,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Sore ga boku no aurora sa\N(That's what my aurora is)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.70,0:46:33.95,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hyakuoku nen tatte mo\N(Though ten billion years may pass,)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.95,0:46:37.83,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Kawaranai hikari de\N(its light will never fade)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.04,0:46:46.11,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Itsumo kimi wo mimamoru kara\N(I will always keep watching over you)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.11,0:46:50.52,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Mayowanaide ikiteite\N(So live out your life without doubts)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.91,0:46:54.25,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Haruka na sora ni\N(In the faraway sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.25,0:46:58.05,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah, kirameku aurora dream\N(Ah, a shining aurora dream)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.05,0:47:04.15,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Itoshii hito yo, sono hitomi de uketomete\N(My dearest, I hope you will notice and accept it)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.15,0:47:06.49,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Miageru sora ni\N(Whenever you look at the sky,)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.49,0:47:10.29,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah, mabushii aurora dream\N(You'll see a dazzling aurora dream)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.29,0:47:12.62,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hitori janai sa\N(You are not alone)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.62,0:47:16.51,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Donna toki mo kono ai wa shine on you\N(My love will always shine on you)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.51,0:47:18.74,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Haruka na sora ni\N(In the faraway sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.74,0:47:22.57,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah, kirameku aurora dream\N(Ah, a shining aurora dream)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.57,0:47:28.69,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Itoshii hito yo, sono hitomi de uketomete\N(My dearest, I hope you will notice and accept it)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.69,0:47:30.94,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Miageru sora ni\N(Whenever you look at the sky,)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.94,0:47:34.81,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah, mabushii aurora dream\N(You'll see a dazzling aurora dream)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.81,0:47:37.12,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Hitori janai sa\N(You are not alone)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.12,0:47:40.96,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Donna toki mo kono ai wa shine on you\N(My love will always shine on you)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.96,0:47:43.17,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Tabitatsu sora ni\N(Whenever you go on a journey,)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.17,0:47:46.17,Singing (TOP),,0,0,0,,Ah, kirameku aurora dream...\N(A shining aurora dream will be seen in the sky...)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer you look,\Nthe more it seems to draw you in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's showing us those beautiful stars\Nbecause our hearts are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really get the Rido with this, Liot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's an ancient lens called the Eye of Zalem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That lens is the key to the Rido lying in Zalem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hurry to Zalem, Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we go to Zygoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Zygoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the owner\Nof the other Eye of Zalem lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me! Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the Eye of Zalem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out that you're a descendant of Zalem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll break your fingers next, one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This one looks more cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man can't hear us very well. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me what\NI want to hear, my young friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave the l-lens to some guy called L-Liot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? To Liot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell me where he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Liot...! Z-Zalem...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come one, come all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and take a closer\Nlook at my wares, dear customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have lots of fine goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My wares are the only reason to come to Zygoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wear this and you'll conquer\Nthe heart of any man you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bored...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Yuta la Caradeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Randall from the\NShirale Valley told me to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Randall? Oh, that Randall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his message.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Eye of Zalem invites misfortune.\NI'd like you to give it to Liot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now give me the lens\Nthat looks just like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot! Do you have to\Nflirt with every girl you meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't flirting with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always treat your customers like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the rude ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!\NGo and do something about this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped you already, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to fight, do it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaiser, give me the status report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the Rido excavation\Nproject in Zalem is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope you won't repeat your past mistakes.\NDon't let Liot overtake you again.{\i0}{lib}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must not fail me this time.\NIf you do, you'll answer for it with your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! I'll live up to your expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spica! Seneca! Keep back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay!\N-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, give me your Eye of Zalem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you,\Nthe only eyes I have are my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The sheer nerve of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary humans like\Nyou can't hope to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!\NTake him out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One against three.\NThe odds aren't in his favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How? They look so formidable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look no further.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-There!\N-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's retreat for now.\NYou shall pay for this, Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a postcard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye! See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid girls! The situation\Nwasn't dangerous enough to use those!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? We thought you were losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? That's no reason\Nto throw the Hiss Candy at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! It seemed\Nlike the best move at the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the bill for\Nthe damages to my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about dodging the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm... We're poor,\Nso how about a monthly payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's only one way I could pay it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give me the Eye of Zalem,\NI'll use it to find a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the secret of the Eye of Zalem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The lens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this to you on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot has thwarted our plans again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you located the other descendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fixated on Liot to\Nthe detriment of everything else....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think Liot went to Zygoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He went there to get the other lens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That means...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The other descendant of Zalem lives in Zygoa,\Nand yet you allowed Liot to get there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you speak of the\Ngirl who works in that store?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Bring that girl to me, \Nalong with the Eye of Zalem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd simply run away\Nunless I kept an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Our journey is full of grave dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect way to stave off boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You never run out of retorts, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a Jigu fruit. You should eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A Jigu fruit? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fruits are very nutritious.\NOne will last you a whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuck! It tastes terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate a Jigu fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Planas' food!\NIt doesn't taste good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Planas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, didn't I tell you about Seneca and Spica?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They belong to another species.\NThey aren't exactly human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They're not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're Planas. In other words,\Nartificial life-forms grown from polytron artificial cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Artificial life-forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two were born to be my partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you three?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ordinary treasure hunters, looking for the treasure of Rido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rido?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the legend\Nof the ancient Quall civilization?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it.\NIt was destroyed several centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient Quall people had a treasure of sorts...\NA type of mineral that can provide infinite energy—Rido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As the legacy of their civilization, the Quall people hid a\Nfew small deposits of that mineral somewhere on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruins of Zalem are one such place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zalem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they wander off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be flirting\Nwith each other as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Liot.\NHe has a thing for girls like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Puru, come closer to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Puru, let's play again some other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do after you find Rido, the treasure of Zalem?\NWill you live the rest of your days in luxury?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettably, that lifestyle doesn't interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type to stay\Nin one place for long, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to fall into the\Nhands of Demster and his gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rido has the power to\Nsave people if it's used correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister was injured in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's suspended in stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the Rido to bring her back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to sleep.\NWe have to get up early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... The entrance to Zalem \Nis supposed to be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There are towers around the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time you paid for your impudence, Liot!{lib}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to save her life,\Nyou'd better give me the lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Put it on the ground and step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your change!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah!\N-Oh, I'm covered in soot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We go after Yuta, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Back into the lake they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But where exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could there be an underwater passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you find the tunnel entrance underwater?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep searching. It's a slow process.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No arguing with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you could detect each other\Nover long distances, like we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Detect each other...? Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You made her eat a Jigu fruit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but she spat it out straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of food...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Yuta la Caradeen.\NOr should I say, Kladinova Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I made detailed inquiries about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered you were\Na descendant of the Priests of Zalem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was easy to find the other four\NZalem descendants. They were all old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't imagine that the owner of the other lens,\Nthe fifth Zalem descendant, would be a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those old men were all tight-mouthed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They could have lived longer,\Nhad they been more obliging.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:22:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad temper is in your blood, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, will you hand \Nover the last Eye of Zalem?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to spare your life, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the juice of the Jigu fruit which Yuta ate contains polytrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Detectable traces will remain in her\N body for the next three or four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I found her, Liot! \NThere's a chasm dead ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.74,0:24:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, the Rido will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.88,0:24:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient Quall writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.31,0:25:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the one who serves me touches the crystal\Nembedded in my forehead, the door of life will be opened."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.86,0:25:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.93,0:25:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"The one who serves me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.71,0:25:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So only the descendants of \NZalem Priests can open the way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.68,0:25:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the girl to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.76,0:25:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.91,0:25:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well be a maze, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.65,0:25:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn right, Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.55,0:25:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.37,0:25:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now turn left!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.23,0:25:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.31,0:26:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could've guessed the\Nexit would be through a waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.09,0:26:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.29,0:26:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. Come on up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.61,0:27:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, touch the crystal before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.74,0:28:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.29,0:28:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't make it in time. \NThe lock to the treasure is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.17,0:28:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grabbing the Rido.\NMy gang will keep you occupied in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.11,0:29:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.10,0:29:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.53,0:29:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.99,0:30:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea the dungeon\Nunder the temple was full of traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.61,0:30:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!\NYou don't need me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.60,0:30:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast. You're staying\Nwith me until I get the Rido.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.67,0:30:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spica!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.71,0:31:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Spica, Seneca—handle the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.28,0:31:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The flow of the water's too fast. In that case...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.61,0:31:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rido, the source of infinite energy\Nthat powered the ancient Quall civilization...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.92,0:31:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I have it, \NI can easily conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.19,0:31:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I {\i1}am{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}the ruler of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.61,0:32:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't going anywhere.\N I'll use you to entrap and kill Liot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.81,0:32:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.77,0:33:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.91,0:33:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.81,0:33:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You shouldn't have\Nremoved the Rido from sacred water!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.89,0:33:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.24,0:33:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you take the Rido from\Nthe sacred water, it begins to release its energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.65,0:33:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words—you made a \Nmistake at the last possible moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Rido, Liot? What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.08,0:33:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.21,0:33:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But we came all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.97,0:33:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We could always look for another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.76,0:33:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, pick up the pace.\NThe underground realm's collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.98,0:33:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.71,0:33:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient Quall people used \Nthe Rido as the core of this realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.64,0:34:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Rido disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.77,0:34:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...this realm collapses likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.35,0:34:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Liot!\N-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! More importantly,\Nlet's get out of here—this realm is collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.35,0:34:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Seneca, summon Puru!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.91,0:34:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I did so long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.42,0:34:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be in the sea nearby.\N I bet he's just messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.41,0:36:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot! You won't get out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.59,0:36:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.75,0:36:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.54,0:37:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Le Deus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.39,0:37:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Deus?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.14,0:37:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.47,0:37:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seneca, Spica—take Yuta and get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.16,0:37:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.92,0:38:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've suffered enough at your hands!\NNow the tables have turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.86,0:38:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.41,0:39:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.50,0:40:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.76,0:40:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.16,0:40:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you got out safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.47,0:40:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.73,0:40:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot! Time and again you thwarted\Nmy plans! Today, I'll return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.96,0:40:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! So you haven't\Ndied with the city of Zalem, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.36,0:40:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to personally finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.05,0:40:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.69,0:41:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.23,0:41:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.39,0:41:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.33,0:41:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's more powerful than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.91,0:41:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Aren't you tired of running yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.69,0:41:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish! The real fight's just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The angels of victory are on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.91,0:41:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Angels, you say? Well, I don't see any!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.75,0:42:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.80,0:42:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.98,0:42:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Synchroid Twin!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.41,0:43:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.94,0:43:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.94,0:43:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.03,0:43:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons selection: Hypersword!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.19,0:43:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.03,0:43:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.80,0:43:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The target is on the move!\NThirty degrees to the left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.54,0:43:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.63,0:43:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weapons selection: Spin Cracker!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.61,0:43:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.91,0:43:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The target is moving again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.54,0:43:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.54,0:44:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seneca, Spica! It's time to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.85,0:44:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.80,0:44:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deploying the ultimate weapon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.17,0:44:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.20,0:44:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The likes of you couldn't defeat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.45,0:44:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.16,0:44:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Done and dusted at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.95,0:44:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nicely done!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.96,0:45:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that,\Nthe Rido was almost within my grasp...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.37,0:45:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such is life. \NWe'll get another chance someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.12,0:45:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.53,0:45:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder—where's Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.24,0:45:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Liot!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.56,0:45:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't going to leave me behind, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.13,0:45:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.76,0:45:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The bill...!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.49,0:45:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I hoped she'd forget about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.59,0:45:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so damn pushy!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.36,0:45:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I'm stuck\Nwith another piece of baggage...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.63,0:45:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you mean by that, Liot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.95,0:45:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, well, see, in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.51,0:45:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be getting bored any time soon.{\i0}
